import '../css/components.css'

export default function ArrowIcon() {
    return (
        <svg 
            className="icon-arrow" 
            aria-hidden="true" 
            viewBox="0 0 37 40">
            <path 
                fill="currentColor" 
                fillRule="evenodd" 
                d="M0 0h18.095L36.19 20 18.095 40H0l17.143-20z">
            </path>
        </svg>
    )
}
